#  AI-Based Smart Navigation System for the Visually Impaired

### Edge AI Obstacle Detection & Voice Guidance using ESP32-S3-CAM, HC-SR04P & YOLOv8

[![Platform](https://img.shields.io/badge/Platform-ESP32--S3-blue?logo=espressif)](https://www.espressif.com/)
[![Language](https://img.shields.io/badge/Firmware-C%2B%2B-00599C?logo=c%2B%2B)](https://en.cppreference.com/)
[![Python](https://img.shields.io/badge/AI%20Server-Python%203-3776AB?logo=python&logoColor=white)](https://www.python.org/)
[![YOLO](https://img.shields.io/badge/Detection-YOLOv8n-purple)](https://github.com/ultralytics/ultralytics)
[![Termux](https://img.shields.io/badge/Runtime-Termux%20(Android)-black?logo=android)](https://termux.dev/)
