##  System Workflow

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    A[ESP32-S3-CAM] --> B[Capture Image / OV2640]
    A --> C[Measure Distance / HC-SR04P]
    C --> D[Median Filter x5]
    D --> E[Compute Warning Level]
    B --> F[MJPEG Stream :81]
    E --> G[Data API :8080/data]
    A --> H[Buzzer Local Alert]

    F --> I[Python Server: Camera Thread]
    G --> J[Python Server: Data Thread]
    I --> K[YOLOv8n Detection Thread]
    K --> L{Confidence ≥ Threshold<br/>AND class in whitelist?}
    L -- No --> M[Discard detection]
    L -- Yes --> N[Annotate frame + collect detection]
    N --> O[Flask Video Feed /video_feed]

    J --> P[Voice Alert Thread]
    N --> P
    P --> Q{distance ≤ 0 or > 1.5m?}
    Q -- Yes --> R[No voice alert]
    Q -- No --> S{Detection available?}
    S -- Yes --> T[Speak object name + direction + distance]
    S -- No --> U[Speak generic obstacle warning]
    T --> V[TTS Queue maxsize=1]
    U --> V
    V --> W[TTSWorker: termux-tts-speak]

    P --> X[Heartbeat Thread: GET /yolo?ok=1]
    X --> A
```

