##  Configuration

### ESP32 Firmware (`main.cpp`)

| Parameter | Default | Description |
|---|---|---|
| `WIFI_SSID` / `WIFI_PASSWORD` | `"Fantom"` / `"00000000"` | Wi‑Fi credentials |
| `CENTER_ANGLE` / `MIN_ANGLE` / `MAX_ANGLE` | `90` / `30` / `150` | Servo sweep range and rest position |
| `SERVO_STEP` / `SERVO_DELAY_MS` | `1` / `15` | Sweep speed (~66°/s) |
| `SONAR_INTERVAL_MS` | `100` | Minimum time between ultrasonic reads |
| `SONAR_TIMEOUT_US` | `30000` | Max wait for echo pulse (~5 m range) |
| `SONAR_FILTER_SIZE` | `5` | Median filter window size |
| `YOLO_TIMEOUT_MS` | `5000` | Time before YOLO heartbeat is considered stale |
| Camera resolution | `VGA` (PSRAM) / `QVGA` (no PSRAM) | Auto-selected based on `psramFound()` |
| JPEG quality | `12` (PSRAM) / `15` (no PSRAM) | Lower number = higher quality, larger size |

### Python AI Server (`main_fixed_termux_yolo.py`)

| Parameter | Default | Description |
|---|---|---|
| `ESP32_IP` | `10.25.87.51` | IP address of the ESP32 on the local network |
| `MODEL_PATH` | `yolov8n.pt` | YOLO weights file |
| `CONF_THRESHOLD` | `0.65` | Minimum detection confidence kept |
| `IOU_THRESHOLD` | `0.45` | Non-max-suppression IoU threshold |
| `CAMERA_TARGET_FPS` | `8.0` | Cap on frame ingestion rate |
| `YOLO_TARGET_FPS` | `2.0` | Cap on inference rate |
| `JPEG_QUALITY` | `80` | Output stream JPEG quality |
| `VOICE_MIN_INTERVAL_SEC` | `3.0` | Minimum gap between spoken alerts |
| `VOICE_MAX_DISTANCE_CM` | `150.0` | Beyond this, no voice alert is spoken |
| `HEARTBEAT_INTERVAL_SEC` | `2.0` | How often `/yolo?ok=1` is pinged |
| `DATA_POLL_INTERVAL_SEC` | `0.2` | How often `/data` is polled |
| `ALLOWED_CLASSES` | 13 classes | Whitelist filtering YOLO output to navigation-relevant objects |
| `FLASK_PORT` | `5000` | Dashboard port |

