</details>

<details>
<summary><strong>GET /video_feed</strong> — Annotated MJPEG stream</summary>
Returns a `multipart/x-mixed-replace; boundary=frame` stream of YOLO-annotated JPEG frames, sourced from `SystemState.get_annotated_jpeg()` (falls back to a placeholder image until the first frame is processed).
</details>

